---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Venus Wafers — Customer Story — Formic"
  description="Nearly a century into making premium crackers and flatbreads, Venus Wafers automated palletizing with Formic — protecting people from repetitive strain without compromising fragile product."
  ogTitle="Venus Wafers — Formic Customer Story"
  ogDescription="Nearly a century in business · 24/7 production · smarter manufacturing"
>
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://formic.co/stories/venus-wafers" slot="head" />

<div class="detail-bc">
  <a href="/">Home</a><span class="sep">/</span><a href="/stories">Customer Stories</a><span class="sep">/</span>Venus Wafers
</div>

<section class="detail-hero">
  <div class="si">
    <div class="slabel" style="color:var(--orange)">Customer Story · Venus Wafers</div>
    <h1 style="font-size:clamp(32px,3.8vw,56px)">Venus Wafers Cracks the Smart Manufacturing Code with Automated Palletizing</h1>
    <p class="lede">Nearly a century into making premium crackers and flatbreads for New England, Venus Wafers automated palletizing with Formic — protecting people from repetitive strain and moving them into more skilled roles, without compromising fragile product.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dark">
  <div class="detail-video wide">
    <div class="detail-video-frame">
      <img src="/stories/venus-wafers-hero.jpg" alt="Venus Wafers cracker production and palletizing" />
      <span class="dv-cap">Venus Wafers · New England</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white" style="padding:64px 0 0">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 80px">
    <div class="db-tag">At a glance</div>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(150px,1fr));gap:1px;background:var(--lgrey);border:1px solid var(--lgrey);margin-top:14px">
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">In business</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">Nearly a century</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Location</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">New England</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Industry</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">Crackers & flatbreads</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Production</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">3 shifts · 24/7</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Brands</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">CäPeachio's, Mariner, South Shore</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white">
  <div class="db-grid">
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">01 — The Challenge</div>
      <h2>A smarter approach to <em>safety and labor</em>.</h2>
      <p>For nearly a century, Venus Wafers has served New England's food-manufacturing community, making premium crackers and flatbreads for brands including CäPeachio's, Mariner, and South Shore. Under new ownership, Plant Manager Nicolas Ribera has led seven years of modernization — and palletizing was the next repetitive-strain task to automate so employees could move into more skilled roles.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>Nearly a century serving New England</li>
        <li>Seven years of plant modernization</li>
        <li>Repetitive-strain palletizing targeted next</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/stories/venus-wafers-2.jpg" alt="Venus Wafers premium cracker packaging" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">Premium crackers & flatbreads</span></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block lgrey">
  <div class="db-grid flip">
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/Talos-0143.jpg" alt="Formic robotic palletizing cell" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">Consistent · gentle on product</span></div>
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">02 — The Solution</div>
      <h2>Consistent stacks, <em>fragile product intact</em>.</h2>
      <p>Automated palletizing standardizes stacking and case handling to protect fragile crackers and minimize waste — and it recently flexed to a customized packing format for a private-label customer. Venus runs three shifts, 24/7, and is exploring case erecting and packing next, along with tighter package-count accuracy.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>Standardized stacking protects fragile product</li>
        <li>Flexed to a custom private-label format</li>
        <li>24/7 three-shift production</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white" style="padding:88px 80px">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:900px;margin:0 auto;padding:0">
    <div class="pull-quote">
      <blockquote>"By evolving how we work, we're opening new doors for our team. Automation helps us protect our people while making operations more efficient."</blockquote>
      <cite>Nicolas Ribera · Plant Manager, Venus Wafers</cite>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dark">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:80px;text-align:center">
    <div class="db-tag" style="justify-content:center">03 — The Outcome</div>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:clamp(40px,5vw,72px);font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.02em;line-height:1;color:var(--white);margin:18px 0 56px">A company-wide commitment <em style="color:var(--orange);font-style:normal">to progress.</em></h2>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:1px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.1)">
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:36px 24px"><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:48px;font-weight:500;color:var(--orange);line-height:1">~100</div><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(240,245,241,.55);margin-top:12px">Years serving New England</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:36px 24px"><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:48px;font-weight:500;color:var(--orange);line-height:1">24/7</div><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(240,245,241,.55);margin-top:12px">Three-shift production</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:36px 24px"><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:48px;font-weight:500;color:var(--orange);line-height:1">7</div><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(240,245,241,.55);margin-top:12px">Years modernizing</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-cta">
  <h2>Crack your own <em>smart-manufacturing code</em>.</h2>
  <div class="btn-row">
    <a href="mailto:sales@formic.co" class="btn-ctadark">Get Started</a>
    <a href="/stories" class="btn-ctawh">More Customer Stories</a>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
